name: Vaudeville Vinnie
Marathon Dancers
Evil Eye Manders aka The Eyes Have It
King Kohl, Emperor of the Underworld
The Feud
The Atomic Bomb aka The End of the World
The Case of the Southpaw Maiden
The Curse of the Ruby
Wanted Dead or Alive - The Spirit

description: The quest for the Apis Bull continues! While Doc fends off a horde of bruiser Neanderthals, the elusive Russian woman gives him the slip. Can he catch her and convince her to share her story? And The Fabulous Five put their survivalist knowledge to the test as they traipse across the unforgiving Russian steppes!
name: Raise the Khan Chapter Four: Cat And Mouse

description: The Doctor and Sir Callum have ridden out to storm the Dread Tower, but what they discovered there casts a new and terrible light on the history of this medieval fantasy world. With Amys life hanging by a thread, the Doctor is running out of time. And the only thing standing between them is... well, it's a really big, fire-breathing dragon controlled by a psychopath. Thats a new one. Matt Sturges, Eisner Award-nominated writer of Jack of Fables, spins this yarn, featuring covers by Mark Buckingham of Miracleman and Fables fame.
name: A Fairytale Life, Part 4

description: Wire Hangers creator/hard-rock musician, Alan Robert, is back for blood with an all-new horror comic series, titled Crawl to Me. The story centers on Ryan, as he struggles to protect his family from what appears to be an evil entity living within their basements crawl space. It is only after a series of violent events occur, when Ryan realizes he must set aside all he believes to be true in order to face his shocking and inevitable reality. This intense thriller will keep you guessing every step of the way. Written and illustrated by Robert, with covers by Robert and Menton3 (Silent Hill: Past Life), plus incentive covers by U.K. artist, David Lupton.

Detective Makoto Sato returns from Monster Island and he's brought some unusual new friends. Heading straight to the corrupt Chief of Police, Sato makes it clear he'll bring justice to the streets of Tokyo no matter what. To prove his point, Sato decides to show off his new partner... MOTHRA! But Sato might be biting off more than he can chew... after all, there's more than one monster in town!

name: The Wronged Man

description: Robin takes it upon himself to explore the dark corners of the new Arkham City--without letting Batman know. His surveillance of a drug operation leads to an unexpected encounter with a very dangerous player. What will have deadlier consequences--his street fight or the Dark Knight's disapproval?
name: Chapter Four: Guardian Angel

description: Even when the sun doesn't shine on the Li'l Depressed Boy, he can count on his Drew Blood to cheer him up. Pack your bags! It's time for a road trip...
name: History of a Boring Town

description:
The fight for free will starts now!

Alpha was the perfect product of Rossum Corporations mind-altering technology, until he snapped, burdened by the dozens of personalities theyd downloaded into his brain. Now the technology has gone viral, turning the entire population into murderous automatons, and its up to the psychotic Alpha and a small group of survivors to save mankind.

Straight from the Dollhouse one-shot written by show writers Tancharoen and Whedon, this new series continues the tale of survivors taking up arms against Rossum.

Fellow Dollhouse show writer Andrew Chambliss (CWs The Vampire Diaries) makes his comics debut, joining Tancharoen and Whedon!

It may be summer and too hot to play outside, but no one's going to stop our beloved Looney Tunes stars from enjoying their favorite sports! What 'toon can resist a good walk spoiled (that's golf to you mugs,) or the beautiful game (that's soccer to the Americans)? The answer is: none of 'em! Join us on the green or on the pitch in the 200th issue of LOONEY TUNES!
name: Hole In Wonderful, Soccer Blocker, Tee For Two

description: The Punisher is locked in a high-security prison, with every inmate in the place out for his blood. When the convicts begin banding together to stage a full-scale prison riot, how will the Punisher survive when all the hate, rage and violence contained within these walls comes bearing down on him alone?
name: Frank, Part 4

description: A lonely stretch of highway. A tiny town in the middle of nowhere. A trio of vicious creatures on a mission of murder and destruction. And all that stands in their way is Vampirella. It's a road-trip through death and horror, as Vampirella, still dealing with the aftermath of her first adventure, faces a threat that may finally be her match.
name: A Murder of Crows

description:
ISSUE FOUR: LOCKDOWN
With Lowesville on complete curfew from the outside world, Trent MacGowan finds himself trapped to face the residents' fury after publishing his outlandish story. Or so he thought: there's no sign of it anywhere online. Is Lowesville really censored from the outside world? And who are the shadowy strangers following Trent?
name: Lockdown

description: Revenge should never be left to the young. As our three teenage samurai leave their ravaged home behind they search for ways to sustain themselves and execute their vengeance. But as young blood boils, rash decisions are made and the consequences can only bring hardship. There are reasons for the laws of Bushido...and Katashi is about to learn more than one of them at the expense of the one he loves most.

The War for the Uncharted Territories continues! Tensions rise as the alliance against the Kkore might have a greater enemyin themselves! But as things seem their darkest, the key to defeating the Kkore may soon be discovered. What is the secret of a peaceful, ancient race only found on a remote planet? From FARSCAPE creator Rockne S. O'Bannon and fan-favorite novelist Keith R.A. DeCandido!
name: The War For the Uncharted Territories Part 9: Divided We Stand

description:
The Witchblade's power dates back to the beginning of time. But there have been other powers through the centuries, and some of them have merely slumbered, awaiting an awakening. Now an ancient goddess arises in New York City, and only Witchblade bearer Sara Pezzini stands against her. Is Sara ready to face a foe that was old when the world was young?

Join longtime writer Ron Marz (Artifacts, Magdalena) and collaborator Stjepan Sejic (Broken Trinity, Angelus) as they charge towards the landmark issue #150!
name: Tiamat, Part 1 of 4

description: The super-powered veterans of World War II are facing a deadly mystery...and it goes all the way back to the top-secret missions they ran behind enemy lines under Captain Americas command! Meanwhile, the Young Avenger shares his old war stories with his granddaughter, Alyssa. Finally, just as the Young Avenger is about to share what could be "the biggest secret of World War 2", with his granddaughter an infamous character makes a surprised appearance. This helps in unraveling the mystery will come from a very tricky source and nothing is what it seems!
name: Soldier - What Did You See?

description: The crossover fans have been clamoring for continues! Its Starborn and Soldier Zero fighting the vanguard of the Pride and the survival of the galaxy hangs in the balance! SUPERMANs Chris Roberson and SPIDER-MANs Khary Randolph bring you a Stan Lee superhero clash of the titans like no other! Worlds collide in this epic conclusion to the second story arc from Stan The Man Lee!

Between husband and wife do not put the ... Groucho . If you even put your finger between the Darrow spouses you can be sure they will cut it off : their living room is a minefield and the bedroom a trench . Yes, the war of the genders, but here you go too far ! The trusty assistant is not worth much as a marriage counselor , but if in the middle is the hand of a witch ... you can do something !
name: Love Story

description: Arabesques of randomness, impossible monsters that overwhelm entire lives, lives that intersect along unpredictable paths ... Can you rewrite the book of destiny? It looks like a very dense text, but between a word and the other lies an infinite space and infinite ways to be walked. Eleanor Drew is looking for the right one, one that can save her from what he read: "You will be killed by Dylan Dog."
name: Il Monastero

description: The Hell's Express is always on time . Its passengers are late , souls affected by the failure , defeated by life. They lost the appointment with their big chance and now it's too late , the train no longer stops . Passing through dark tunnels and valleys populated by nightmares , he travels like a rocket straight to the final station.
name: Il treno dei dannati

description: From what does mysterious Ishar escape? Who is hunting her? She comes from another world and another time. She was born in a brutal universe of which she has only a vague memory. Now she must go back there , to find herself and her people . Dylan will have to accompany her, among people with amazing powers , knights and sorcery , in a land ruled by magic.
name: La preda umana

description: Fortune is blind , but bad luck is not: Groucho, taken by surprise in a moment of laborious idleness , is struck by the anathemas of OdoacreSinnutti ,a professionalominous raven...
name: Il cavaliere di sventura

description: This time Dylan is the assistant and Groucho the detective: obviously something went wrong ! The cause is the picture of Lord Crooked , marked by the ancient curse of wrongness . Try to straighten it and you will see the world turned upside down, so that a vicious serial killer can even become... a serial lover !
name: Sotto il vestito troppo

description: A steel giant lies in the ocean: the Goliath Oil Platform no longer gives signs of life , like a super - technological abandoned house in the middle of nowhere . Now it's up to Dylan Dog to face the mystery. Something has risen from the bowels of the Earth to take the body and soul of the crew . A primordial force , , a subtle and deadly being who survived for millennia !
name: Goliath

description: After last issues mind-blowing revelation of the true identity of Death Queen, the next chapter of LADY DEATH begins! Drawn back to the Under Realm after her banishment to Earth, Lady Death has returned, but she is a shadow of her former self and still not in possession of her full power. That power lies in the hands of Death Queen, who has ripped her greatest nemesis through the dimension-spanning breach for one very specific purpose: To fuel the enormous Infernal Engine will could wipe out all life in the entire Under Realm! Its the battle youve been waiting for, as Wargoth takes on the monstrous Behemoth, the Demon-led rebellion launches an attack against the zombie hordes guarding the Infernal Engine and Lady Death goes head-to-head with Death Queen in the most emotional and vicious battle of her life! Co-written by Mike (Gravel, Wolfskin) Wolfer and original creator Brian Pulido, this series promises to be the most powerful Lady Death tale ever! This arc features the art of amazing new talent Gabriel Andrade who also provides the Regular and Wraparound covers for this issue! Also available with a special Art Deco Retailer Order Incentive by painter Michael Dipascale!

An experiment with unpredictable results, a formula that is tempting intelligence services around the world and an amazing new source of energy. To counteract what, in the wrong hands, could become a weapon of unimaginable destructive power, Dylan Dog faces mysterious creatures made of pure light.
name: Il Padrone della Luce

description: Ahab has returned and resumed , more deadly than ever,the hunt for Moby Dick! Will the new Pequod follow the same fate as its predecessor, or this time the unquenchable hatred of Ahab will defeat the whale? Dylan, embarked against his will, cannot help but watch and wait for the encounter with the majestic Lady of the Sea.
name: Sulla rotta di Moby Dick

description: A day like all others, for Groucho ... shopping at the market, a jump at the news store and then home. Well, it would be a day like the others if at 7 of Craven Road there would still be the home of Dylan Dog, with the attached Investigator of nightmare, and not rather a low class bar run by a guy who claims to be there for at least sixteen years. For Groucho and inspector Bloch it seems to be no way to solve the mystery, as long as for Lord H. G. Wells, until one of his improbable gadgets can detect an emanation of waves of negativity, the origin of which, though invisible, is right under everyone's eyes.
name: Dov finito Dylan Dog?

description: On a small island , not far from the place where Dylan Dog said goodbye to his old friend, Birdy , some witnesses claim to have seen a mysterious " bird man " at the head of an army of birds. For the Old Boy to uncover the truth about this story is a personal matter that will take him in the middle of a bloody war.
name: Il santuario

description: Saul, the Angel of Death, is back alongside Dylan to fight the dangerous sect of the Illuminati that the Investigator of nightmare thought he had finally defeated. The new threat now concerns the new world that will rise from the ashes of the old one, after an apocalypse that neither Dylan can prevent.
name: L'angelo caduto

description: Jacques Leduc , the brave captain of the Scylla , after having spent his whole life trying to prove the existence of " Mermaids ," leaves to his daughter Charlotte a dossier containing a photography of one of them . Dylan and the girl leave for the island of Legtail , where they meet an ancient horror emerging from the depths of the abyss .
name: Profondo blu

description:
The long-awaited second chapter of Alan Moore and Kevin O'Neill's League of Extraordinary Gentlemen III: Century takes place almost sixty years later in the psychedelic daze of Swinging London during 1969, a place where Tadukic Acid Diethylamide 26 is the drug of choice, and where different underworlds are starting to overlap dangerously to an accompaniment of sit-ins and sitars. Alerted to a threat concerning the same magic order that she and her colleagues were investigating during 1910, a thoroughly modern Mina Murray and her dwindling league of comrades attempt to navigate the perilous rapids of London's hippie and criminal subculture, as well as the twilight world of its occultists. Mina and her companions must prevent the making of a Moonchild that might well turn out to be the Anti-Christ.

CHAPTER TWO takes place almost sixty years later in the psychedelic daze of Swinging London during 1969, a place where Tadukic Acid Diethylamide 26 is the drug of choice, and where different underworlds are starting to overlap dangerously to an accompaniment of sit-ins and sitars. The vicious gangster bosses of London's East End find themselves brought into contact with a counter-culture underground of mystical and medicated flower-children, or amoral pop-stars on the edge of psychological disintegration and developing a taste for Satanism. Alerted to a threat concerning the same magic order that she and her colleagues were investigating during 1910, a thoroughly modern Mina Murray and her dwindling league of comrades attempt to navigate the perilous rapids of London's hippy and criminal subculture, as well as the twilight world of its occultists. Starting to buckle from the pressures of the twentieth century and the weight of their own endless lives, Mina and her companions must nevertheless prevent the making of a Moonchild that might well turn out to be the antichrist.
name: 1969: Paint it Black

volume.name: The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen: Century

description: On returning from Scotland , Dylan Dog 's car breaks down suddenly in the midst of a forest and he finds himself struggling to survive in the middle of a mysterious off-season snowstorm . Forced to take refuge in what seems a classic haunted house , the Investigator of Nightmares will end up facing a far more frightening horror: a surreal live broadcast from which the Old Boys will have only one way to escape : to wait with the others the inevitable final elimination!
name: Reality Show

description: Glendoune is a pleasant Scottish village , known for raising sheep , but also for the annual festival dedicated to the fascinating and disturbing figure of the werewolf . Dylan has been invited by the organizers to keep a conference , but lost in the fog that prevails on the moors , she finds himself near Cameron House , a few miles from his goal . Guest of Alec and Emma Cameron 's, the " nightmare investigator " will learn that the life of civilized man and that of the wild wolf have many things in common .
name: Licantropia

description: Dylan Dog is called as " special advisor " from cult director Blake Kline , who wants to shoot in an old manor on the Carpathian Mountains the remake of " The fortress of the demon ", a horror classic of the '30s . But the magic of the set will soon turn into tragedy ...
name: La fortezza del demone

description: Death, an old friend of Dylan Dog, shows him what would happen if in the important moments of his life he had made different choices.
name: La scelta

description: Mysterious and monstrous genetic mutations affect the inhabitants of London, and the city falls into total panic...has the plague of the third millennium come?
name: La peste

description: On the streets of Old Canterbury an encounter with a dying girl pushes Brendon to cross the borders of Darkdom , on the edge of hell .
name: La sposa in nero

description: After having lost themselves in an unknown galaxy, Jack, April, Helen and all the other members of the crew of Argos Asteroid will face their first mission in the new galaxy, where a war between two alien races is enraging.
name: Il pianeta delle sabbie

description: Returned from the planet Tipu, the crew of the asteroid Argo the makes its way to the planet Kundingas As the Major Sheldon and Rick Brice are engaged in official matters , Lieutenant Obaru and April Frayn decide to take a short vacation . Holiday fun will be less and shorter than expected , when their guide on the planet is found murdered and they are blamed for the crime.
name: Gli esploratori dello spazio

description: As a result of a rare cosmic phenomenon , the Asteroid Argo and its weird crew were thrown in a galaxy light-years away from Earth . Major Sheldon , Lieutenant Obaru , Rick Brice , Professor Anderson and android McCloud , along with the two Alfa agents Jack O'Ryan and April Frayn arrive in the Kuaddhar Belt , on the planet Raikuu, fought between the race of Triekuu and that of Baikuu , to answer the distress call of a mysterious civilization that was believed to be disappeared thousands of years before ...
name: Il pianeta degli schiavi

description: Argo Asteroid receives a request for help by Dr. Talaak, leader of a scientific mission that is running studies of genetic mutations of the vegetation on the planet Nekaff and has been hit by a strong magnetic storm. While seeking shelter , the doctor and his assistant meet three dying nekafiti. One of them, shortly before his death , gives them a mysterious box that contains some spores to be protected. After reaching the scientists , Jack O'Ryan must find a way to bring everyone to safety , after revealing the enigma of the spores and finding a cure for Major Sheldon , hit by a deadly parasite , and now in serious life danger.
name: Un nuovo inizio

description: Anthology comic from the Cartoon Militia.

Nvis participe au Cannonball de l'espace, une course illgale o tous les coups sont permis et son seul moyen pour rejoindre discrtement Bobo. Elle compte lui demander pourquoi il lui a menti et qu'il lui rvle qui la finanait clandestinement pendant qu'elle tait agent de Sillage... Drapages verbaux incontrls et prises de risques maximales seront au programme de cette course la vrit.
name: Drapage contrl
The Iron Tower
Eye of the Sea
The Isle of Dwarves

description: As graduation approaches, Amu's guardians, Ran, Miki, and Su disappear. Led by Diamond, Amu takes a journey on the road of stars to find her missing guardians. Will Amu find her guardians or will she find more then she could have expected?
name: Vol. 11

description: After a dramatic confrontation with the evil pirate Shiuba, Raizo parts ways with Tsunami. He meets a lovely missionary known as Anjo, or Angel. Raizo begins to fall in love with the selfless and generous Angel. Will Raizo and Angel end up on cloud nine or will kabuki Seigan find yet another way to ruin Raizo's heavenly hopes?
name: Did It Hurt... When You Fell From Heaven?

description:
IN THE SHADOW OF THE MOON

Tsubasa hunt for The King thickens when Arisa's class goes to a planetarium to watch an eclipse and The King makes a decree that turns the chosen against each other. Later, suspicion mounts on Midori, who asks Tsubasa on a date! Can Tsubasa save the day from The King, and protect the stars in her sister's sky from ill fates?

Includes special extras after the story!
name: Vol. 3

description: On behalf of the Security Council the Alfa Agency is charged with investigating after an incident that knocked out a base in the Arctic, run by Halicox pharmaceutical company to perform medical research. Nathan, Nicole, Branko and May leave for the Arctic, accompanied by a physician from the company.
name: Base Artica

description: In a base infested by zombie- soldiers , Nathan rescues a still healthy woman that recognizes the doctor , who is forced to confess all the background story. Unfortunately for the team, the unexpected is lurking . One of the zombie soldiers manages to hit Branko with a gunshot wounding him deadly. The only way to save him is to inject the same Stillframe serum who started it all.
name: Prigionieri di un incubo

description: The Alfa Agency is sent to recover a mysterious object in a bank that is in an areaof East City that was destroyed after the fall of Urania ,and has now suddenly reappeared in space .
name: Morte nello spazio

description: Shinji Soudas not exactly happy about his familys age-old marriage customs, namely the fact that he has to marry a boy! Will a sudden confession from his bride-to-be, a beautiful boy in his class named Aoi, make Shinji change his mind? This sweet love story follows the couple through their marriage ceremony, wedding night, life as newlyweds, and even childbirth! The title story in this compilation is the prequel to Mr. Flower Groom, also being published by Yen Press.
name: Vol. 1

description: Myung-Ee decides to rescue Yu-Da from the Fox Tribe! She begins by journeying to Junghyun Mountain to join the Soon-La Army. But first she must pass a test of pain and endurance. Meanwhile, more secrets are revealed about the kind and gentle Yu-Da...
name: Vol. 2
